European Stocks Extend Gain as Libya Says It Will Halt Military Operations

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-03-18T12:43:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/european-stocks-extend-gain-as-libya-says-it-will-halt-military-operations.html
European stocks extended their
advance as the Libyan foreign minister said the nation will halt
all military action. The Stoxx Europe 600 Index climbed 0.8
percent to 269.13 at 12:43 p.m. in  London .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
